{"data":[{"name":"94:1","price":"Bukankah kami telah melapangkan dadamu (Muhammad)?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَشۡرَحۡ لَكَ صَدۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6091,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"alam nashraḥ laka ṣadraka ","translations":["Have not","We expanded","for you","your breast","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["alam","nashraḥ","laka","ṣadraka",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,750],[2,750,1500],[3,1500,1960],[4,1960,3515]]}},{"name":"94:2","price":"Dan kami pun telah menurunkan beban darimu,913)","arabic":"وَوَضَعۡنَا عَنكَ وِزۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6092,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"*913) Kesusahan-kesusahan yang diderita Nabi Muhammad -ṣallallāhu 'alaihi wa sallam- dalam menyampaikan risalah.","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"wawaḍaʿnā ʿanka wiz'raka ","translations":["And We removed","from you","your burden","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wawaḍaʿnā","ʿanka","wiz'raka",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1350],[2,1350,2970],[3,2970,4315]]}},{"name":"94:3","price":"yang memberatkan punggungmu,","arabic":"ٱلَّذِيٓ أَنقَضَ ظَهۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6093,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī anqaḍa ẓahraka ","translations":["Which","weighed upon","your back","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","anqaḍa","ẓahraka",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2700],[2,2700,4140],[3,4140,5465]]}},{"name":"94:4","price":"dan kami tinggikan sebutan (nama)mu914) bagimu.","arabic":"وَرَفَعۡنَا لَكَ ذِكۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6094,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"*914) Meninggikan derajat dan menggandengkan namanya dengan nama Allah dalam kalimat syahadat, menjadikan taat kepada Nabi termasuk taat kepada Allah.","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"warafaʿnā laka dhik'raka ","translations":["And We raised high","for you","your reputation","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["warafaʿnā","laka","dhik'raka",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1410],[2,1410,1830],[3,1830,3465]]}},{"name":"94:5","price":"Maka sesungguhnya bersama kesulitan ada kemudahan,","arabic":"فَإِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرًا","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6095,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-inna maʿa al-ʿus'ri yus'ran ","translations":["So indeed","with","the hardship","(is) ease","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-inna","maʿa","al-ʿus'ri","yus'ran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1640],[2,1640,2010],[3,2010,2850],[4,2850,4445]]}},{"name":"94:6","price":"sesungguhnya bersama kesulitan ada kemudahan.","arabic":"إِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرٗا","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6096,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"inna maʿa al-ʿus'ri yus'ran ","translations":["Indeed","with","the hardship","(is) ease","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","maʿa","al-ʿus'ri","yus'ran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1400],[2,1400,1780],[3,1780,2650],[4,2650,4125]]}},{"name":"94:7","price":"Maka apabila engkau telah selesai (dari suatu urusan), tetaplah bekerja keras (untuk urusan yang lain),915)","arabic":"فَإِذَا فَرَغۡتَ فَٱنصَبۡ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6097,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"*915) Sebagian mufasir menafsirkan apabila engkau (Muhammad) telah selesai berdakwah maka beribadahlah kepada Allah; apabila engkau telah selesai melaksanakan urusan dunia maka kerjakanlah urusan akhirat dan ada lagi yang mengatakan, \"Apabila telah mengerjakan salat maka berdoalah\".","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-idhā faraghta fa-inṣab ","translations":["So when","you have finished","then labor hard","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-idhā","faraghta","fa-inṣab",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,850],[2,850,1730],[3,1730,3565]]}},{"name":"94:8","price":"dan hanya kepada Tuhanmulah